<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11875</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17461</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡拉巴斯很穷。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17461</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的屋顶有洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23522</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的衣服有洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的鞋子也有洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42141</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每天早晨，卡拉巴斯都在菜园里干活。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42141</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45820</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好，卡拉巴斯！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45820</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴蒂斯塔牵着驴走过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡拉巴斯挥挥手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53862</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡拉巴斯看了看西红柿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎！” 他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64997</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个西红柿被虫子咬了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64997</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68239</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>另一个烂掉了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68239</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，一个苹果从路上滚了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77899</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡拉巴斯捡起苹果。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77899</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81078</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>苹果又红又大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81078</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84383</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他舔了舔嘴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84383</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，卡拉巴斯看到一个人推着一车苹果。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95373</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跟着跑了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100272</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您掉了一个苹果！” 卡拉巴斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100272</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109154</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个人说了谢谢。“你很诚实！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109154</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114570</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡拉巴斯去了小镇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他买了一块面包。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123532</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，他听到音乐声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123532</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128641</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡拉巴斯往咖啡厅里看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128641</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133297</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个人在弹吉他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133297</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137946</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡拉巴斯闭上了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137946</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“多美妙的音乐啊。” 他想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁边有几个人在聊天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145423</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148626</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你听说了吗？” 一个人问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148626</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“食人魔从山上下来了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都吓了一跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163673</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡拉巴斯很害怕。“食人魔现在在哪里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163673</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168861</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个人耸耸肩。“没人知道。” 他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168861</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173361</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“食人魔很可怕的。” 一个女人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173361</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175838</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今晚我要锁好门！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175838</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡拉巴斯赶紧回家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185283</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他也要锁好门！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>